@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: Metadata Operations (mkdir, ls, mv)

actor Client
participant "Metadata Server\n(Master)" as Master

== Directory Creation (mkdir) ==
Client -> Master: Request Mkdir (Path, Auth Token)
activate Master
Master -> Master: Validate Token
Master -> Master: Insert new directory record in DB
Master --> Client: 201 Created
deactivate Master

== List Contents (ls) ==
Client -> Master: Request List (Path, Auth Token)
activate Master
Master -> Master: Validate Token
Master -> Master: Query DB for files/folders in Path
Master --> Client: 200 OK (List of contents & metadata)
deactivate Master

== Move/Rename (mv) ==
Client -> Master: Request Move (Source Path, Dest Path, Auth Token)
activate Master
Master -> Master: Validate Token
Master -> Master: Update DB record (Change parent ID or name)
Master --> Client: 200 OK (Move successful)
deactivate Master

@enduml
